org.bytedeco.depthai

Class Path

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer
      • org.bytedeco.depthai.Path
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable

    @Namespace(value="dai")
 @NoOffset
 @Properties(inherit=depthai.class)
public class Path
extends Pointer
    \brief Represents paths on a filesystem; accepts utf-8, Windows utf-16 wchar_t, or std::filesystem::path. It is suitable for direct use with OS APIs. Features are limited to character-set conversion of paths. It is not intended as a full replacement for std::filesystem::path
